The Concordance of Research is used for making practice RUNES for all INT casters (Wiz, Mage, Necro, Ench).  There is an "evil" version of the quest based out of South Ro as well as a "good" version based in North Karana.  I did practice runes on my wizzy for a while, but when it got to be more time consuming than it was worth (Probably around skill 100), I switched to real runes and trainer points as has been suggested.

The Lexicon is the Wizzy book for research.  The Warlock's Book of Binding is for Necros from LOY for high level research and making WIS caster spells.  IIRC, you can't get it until you have a skill level around 100 or 110 in research though.


